---
import InvestLayout from '../layouts/InvestLayout.astro';
import Disclosure from '../components/Disclosure.astro';
---

<InvestLayout
  title="Impact"
  titleVi="Tác động"
  description="Nguyen AI Computer impact: community empowerment, bilingual education, heritage preservation, economic opportunity, and privacy-first values."
>
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16" aria-label="Impact overview">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-gold-gradient">Impact</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-xl text-ink-muted" lang="vi">Tác động</p>

    <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-ink-muted max-w-3xl">
      Nguyen AI Computer is built to empower one of the world's largest surname communities with AI-native, privacy-first, bilingual tools.
      <span class="block mt-2" lang="vi">Nguyen AI Computer xây dựng để trao quyền cho một trong những cộng đồng họ lớn nhất thế giới.</span>
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-12">
      {[
        { icon: '🤝', title: 'Community Empowerment', vi: 'Trao quyền cộng đồng', desc: 'Nguyen Chapters, Nguyen Founders, and Nguyen Network give the community tools to organize, connect, and collaborate — not just consume technology.' },
        { icon: '📚', title: 'Bilingual Education', vi: 'Giáo dục song ngữ', desc: 'edu.nguyenai.net provides free AI learning in Vietnamese and English. Certification programs build skills and credibility for the community.' },
        { icon: '🌳', title: 'Heritage Preservation', vi: 'Bảo tồn di sản', desc: 'Nguyen Roots, Nguyen Memory, and Nguyen Knowledge preserve family histories, documents, and oral traditions with evidence-based methodology — no bloodline claims.' },
        { icon: '💼', title: 'Economic Opportunity', vi: 'Cơ hội kinh tế', desc: 'AI Founder OS, AI Business OS, and AI Sales tools give Nguyen founders and businesses access to enterprise-grade AI at accessible price points.' },
        { icon: '🔒', title: 'Privacy-First', vi: 'Riêng tư là trên hết', desc: 'Living-person data is private by default. Family trees are private by default. Each user owns their data vault. PDPD 91/2025 compliance is a feature, not a burden.' },
      ].map((item) => (
        <div class="bg-bg-card border border-bg-border rounded-xl p-6 card-hover">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">{item.icon}</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink">{item.title}</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gold" lang="vi">{item.vi}</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mt-3">{item.desc}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- Ethics note -->
    <div class="mt-12 bg-bg-card border border-gold/20 rounded-xl p-6">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-serif font-bold text-gold mb-2">Ethics & Historical Boundaries</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted" lang="vi">Đạo đức & ranh giới lịch sử</p>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-ink-muted">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-gold mt-0.5">▸</span> Never imply all Nguyen people share one bloodline, descend from Nguyễn Bặc, or belong to the Nguyễn Phúc imperial lineage.</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-gold mt-0.5">▸</span> Never claim AI can confirm ancestry, royal lineage, or bloodline. Use evidence labels and uncertainty language.</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-gold mt-0.5">▸</span> "Nguyen Operating Profile" refers to an operating profile and value system — NOT bloodline, genetics, or superiority.</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-gold mt-0.5">▸</span> Required evidence labels: verified, primary source, secondary source, according to branch genealogy, oral history, insufficient evidence, disputed, cannot conclude.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Impact metrics (hypothesis) -->
    <div class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-ink mb-4">Impact Metrics (Hypothesis) / Chỉ số tác động (giả thuyết)</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        {[
          { value: '4M+', label: 'Nguyen people globally', vi: 'Người họ Nguyễn toàn cầu' },
          { value: '10', label: 'Edu tracks free', vi: 'Track học miễn phí' },
          { value: '9', label: 'Specialized Agents', vi: 'Agent chuyên biệt' },
          { value: '100%', label: 'Privacy-by-default', vi: 'Riêng tư mặc định' },
        ].map((m) => (
          <div class="bg-bg-card border border-bg-border rounded-xl p-5 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-gold">{m.value}</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-ink-muted mt-1">{m.label}</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-ink-dim" lang="vi">{m.vi}</div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-ink-dim italic">All metrics are hypotheses based on public demographic data. Not a forecast. <span lang="vi">Tất cả là giả thuyết, không phải dự báo.</span></p>
    </div>

    <!-- SDG alignment -->
    <div class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-ink mb-4">UN SDG Alignment / Phù hợp SDG Liên Hợp Quốc</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        {[
          { num: '4', title: 'Quality Education', vi: 'Giáo dục chất lượng', desc: 'Free bilingual AI education at edu.nguyenai.net — 10 tracks, certification, accessible to all subscribers.' },
          { num: '8', title: 'Decent Work & Economic Growth', vi: 'Việc làm & tăng trưởng', desc: 'AI Founder OS and AI Business OS give Nguyen founders and businesses enterprise-grade tools at accessible prices.' },
          { num: '9', title: 'Industry, Innovation & Infrastructure', vi: 'Đổi mới & hạ tầng', desc: 'Four-layer AI Computer architecture — a new category of cloud computing specialized for a community.' },
        ].map((sdg) => (
          <div class="bg-bg-card border border-bg-border rounded-xl p-5">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <span class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gold/10 text-gold flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">{sdg.num}</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink text-sm">{sdg.title}</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-gold" lang="vi">{sdg.vi}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted">{sdg.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Community quote -->
    <div class="mt-12 bg-bg-card border border-gold/20 rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
      <blockquote class="text-xl font-serif text-ink-muted italic max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        "We build not for bloodline, but for a community that shares a name, a history, and a future. Nguyen AI Computer is a tool for that future — private by default, bilingual by design, evidence-based by principle."
      </blockquote>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gold">— Nguyen AI Founder Statement</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12"><Disclosure /></div>
  </section>
</InvestLayout>
